p-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498627" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/marvels-spider-man-2-new-details-state-of-play-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498627" class="wp-caption-text"> 《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》图片来源：索尼</figcaption></figure><p>购买游戏数字豪华版的玩家还将获得该版本独有的另外 10 套套装。这些都是 Insomniac Games 邀请漫画、游戏和电影领域的艺术家为蜘蛛侠的英雄主义提供创意的成果。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/immortals-of-aveum"><em>《Immortals Of Aveum》</em></a>商业表现不佳， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ascendant-studios">Ascendant Studios</a>不得不<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/immortals-of-aveum-developer-loses-45-per-cent-of-staff-due-to-poor-sales-3498537">裁掉近一半的员工</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/marvels-spider-man-2-map-will-be-nearly-double-the-first-games-size-3498607">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》后的地图将是</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次出现的第一部游戏的“几乎两倍”。</p> ;
