斯 (Toyah Wilcox) 将于 2022 年 8 月 11 日在费尔波特 Cropredy Convention Festival 上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-fripp">罗伯特·弗里普</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/toyah-willcox">托亚·威尔考克斯</a>的病毒式“周日午餐”活动还远未结束，这对夫妇透露，该系列剧目前正在大银幕上重新制作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/toyah-willcox-robert-fripp-glastonbury-2023-sunday-lunch-tour-interview-david-bowie-3461724">Toyah 和 Robert Fripp 谈论 2023 年格拉斯顿伯里周日午餐的未来</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-crimson">King Crimson</a>成员和他 80 年代流行音乐明星的配偶自 2020 年以来凭借 YouTube 系列“周日午餐”而声名大噪，这对夫妇翻唱了各种摇滚和金属经典歌曲，在该系列节目中广为人知。</p><p>现在，在该项目开始三年后，威尔科克斯（化名托亚）确认会议远未结束，并已被一家计划制作该项目的“大型制作公司”接手。拍成故事片。</p><p> She announced the plans in a new interview with <a href="https://www.eonmusic.co.uk/toyah-wilcox-eonmusic-interview-september-2023.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Eonmusic</em></a> , explaining that momentum has continuously grown since they began the project in lockdown, and is now on the cusp of moving to new heights.</p><p> “We have a documentary crew following us, and we have quite a big production company scripting an idea at the moment,” she said.</p><p> “Obviously, we won&#39;t be in it,” she added. “It&#39;s for actors to play, but that&#39;s all in the back kind of pool of what you call pre-production. All of that&#39;s going on.” </p><figure id="attachment_3498629" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3498629" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498629" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Robert Fripp (L) and Toyah of Toyah &amp; Robert Fripp perform on Day 4 of Wickham Festival 2023 on August 06, 2023" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Robert-Fripp-Toyah-Willcox@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498629" class="wp-caption-text"> Robert Fripp (L) and Toyah of Toyah &amp; Robert Fripp perform on Day 4 of Wickham Festival 2023 on August 06, 2023. CREDIT: Harry Herd/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> The comments in the recent interview build upon a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/toyah-willcox-robert-fripp-glastonbury-2023-sunday-lunch-tour-interview-david-bowie-3461724">discussion the duo had with <em>NME</em> earlier this year</a> , when they arrived for a set at this year&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">Glastonbury</a> festival.</p><p> “We&#39;ve actually been picked up by a world agency and we have decided that we&#39;re going to give them a set amount of years,” Toyah responded when asked how long they see the series continuing for. “At the moment our social media numbers are growing. So as long as those audiences are there and that kind of pull is there, we&#39;ll keep going. But I will not watch him do anything that makes his health suffer.”</p><p> She continued, confirming that they were already underway with three potential television projects at the time: “Another bit of news that&#39;s happening is we&#39;re being courted by TV at the moment. We&#39;ve got about three ideas in the very embryonic form that we should be shooting next year.”</p><p> In other Fripp and Willcox news, last month the couple <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/toyah-willcox-and-robert-fripp-cover-the-hives-for-sunday-lunch-3489443">made headlines after covering The Hives</a> on their viral YouTube series.</p><p> Here, they performed their own version of the Swedish indie rock band&#39;s biggest hit, &#39;Hate To Say I Told You So&#39;, while Fripp dressed as a bee.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robert-fripp-and-toyah-willcoxs-viral-sunday-lunch-sessions-to-be-turned-into-a-movie-or-two-3498625">Robert Fripp and Toyah Willcox&#39;s viral &#39;Sunday Lunch&#39; sessions to be turned into a movie (or two)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
